quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,THE DISASTER
  101,2,What is the Disaster
  101,3,Would that you knew what the Disaster is
  101,4,On that day people shall become like scattered moths
  101,5,and the mountains like tufts of carded wool
  101,6,Then he whose good deeds weigh heavy in the scales
  101,7,shall live in bliss
  101,8,but he whose good deeds are light
  101,9,the Abyss shall be his home
  101,10,Would that you knew what this is like
  101,11,It is a scorching fire